btrplace.json.JSONConverterException

  • Packages that use JSONConverterException 
    Package Description
    btrplace.json
    This package contains the material to convert btrplace primitives to the JSON format and vice-versa.
    btrplace.json.model
    Converters for a model and its sub-components.
    btrplace.json.model.constraint
    Converters for the constraints.
    btrplace.json.model.view
    Converters for the views.
    btrplace.json.plan
    Converters for a plan and its sub-components.
